    {
      "id": "235ff99e-6a9c-4adc-aae6-c34d21c5c809",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$S_n = \\sum_{q=0}^\\infty\\sum_{r=1}^{n-1}\n                       \\frac r{(qn+r)(qn+r+1)}\n                  = \\sum_{q=0}^\\infty\\sum_{r=1}^{n-1}\n                       \\frac r{qn+r} - \\frac r{qn+r+1}$.\n                  \\par\n             $S_n = \\sum_{q=0}^\\infty \\left(\\frac 1{qn+1} + \\frac 1{qn+2}\n                       + \\dots + \\frac 1{qn+n} - \\frac 1{q+1}\\right)\n                  = \\lim_{N\\to\\infty}\\left(\\sum_{k=1}^{(N+1)n} \\frac 1k\n                       - \\sum_{k=1}^{N+1} \\frac 1k \\right)\n                  = \\ln n$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(S_n = \\sum_{q=0}^\\infty\\sum_{r=1}^{n-1}\n                       \\frac r{(qn+r)(qn+r+1)}\n                  = \\sum_{q=0}^\\infty\\sum_{r=1}^{n-1}\n                       \\frac r{qn+r} - \\frac r{qn+r+1}\\)</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(S_n = \\sum_{q=0}^\\infty \\left(\\frac 1{qn+1} + \\frac 1{qn+2}\n                       + \\dots + \\frac 1{qn+n} - \\frac 1{q+1}\\right)\n                  = \\lim_{N\\to\\infty}\\left(\\sum_{k=1}^{(N+1)n} \\frac 1k\n                       - \\sum_{k=1}^{N+1} \\frac 1k \\right)\n                  = \\ln n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
